  "description": "Synchronize Page Content with wesolenutki.eu Reference Site\n\nUpdate and align the current page's content to match the structure, layout, and information presented on the reference website at https://wesolenutki.eu/.\n\nRequirements:\n- Fetch and analyze the content structure from https://wesolenutki.eu/\n- Compare current page content with the reference site to identify differences\n- Update text content, headings, and copy to match the reference\n- Align visual layout including sections, spacing, and component arrangement\n- Ensure images, icons, and media assets match or are equivalent to the reference\n- Preserve any existing functionality while updating the presentation layer\n- Maintain responsive design across all device sizes\n- Verify that styling (colors, fonts, button styles) is consistent with the reference\n- Test all links and interactive elements for proper functionality\n- Ensure any forms or user input fields match the reference implementation\n\nEdge cases to consider:\n- Handle dynamic content that may differ between environments\n- Preserve any site-specific customizations that shouldn't be overwritten\n- Consider language/localization differences if applicable\n- Verify that external dependencies (scripts, fonts, APIs) are properly included",
